{"id": 2862, "genre": 1000, "title": "如果可以的话，你觉得自己最需要哪些小型“线上权利”？", "description": "也可以理解成，生活在当代，你觉得自己基本告别了哪些“线上权利”。（题图来自：视觉中国 ©️ Jane_Kelly）", "record_count": 17970, "comment_count": 44, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190325153103QIunrgZmsJ4qFPKG.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-03-26T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5575, "title": "如果可以的话，你觉得自己最需要哪些小型“线上权利”？", "content": "现如今你觉得自己最需要哪些小型“线上权利”？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 335373, "content": "离线权：不用随时在线，下班时间允许“已读不回”", "image": "img/option/option/20190325173852CtoIPwl05QjUpyZ3.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 335374, "content": "表态权：不是 xx 的粉丝，也可以评价 ta 的作品而不被杠", "image": "img/option/option/20190325174042etxTS8o1aZ0PvN6A.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 335375, "content": "被遗忘权：自己删掉的动态/照片，不留任何线上痕迹", "image": "img/option/option/20190325173905neDO1tc3lYF56p89.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 335376, "content": "知情权：不是不能用我的数据，至少告诉我用了些啥", "image": "img/option/option/20190325174114IMG4sQUrxA89ctR5.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 335377, "content": "不知情权：不想看的八卦/热点/老梗，可以彻底屏蔽", "image": "img/option/option/20190325173748IVGeiTj0qBdDH3az.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 335378, "content": "消失权：已注册的账号提供“删除/注销账户”这个选项", "image": "img/option/option/20190325173648z4ijLbAy1a7EmGvD.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 335379, "content": "自闭权：不参加“打招呼/排行榜”之类的强行社交功能", "image": "img/option/option/20190325175056LU6iCf9WeKZS5FYx.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 335401, "content": "不提示权：默认关闭所有促销/推送，需要我会自己开", "image": "img/option/option/20190325173959B6Yi1zLGNF2EVtkC.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}